label: icaoCode
comment: The International Civil Aviation Organization (ICAO) code assigned to the category of drone corresponding to this observation.

label: droneType
comment: The type of drone categorised by its size or payload capacity or flight distance or wing type etc.

label: purposeCode
comment: The unique code representing the purpose of entity or service corresponding to this observation.

label: purposeDescription
comment: Describes the purpose of the entity or service corresponding to this observation.

label: registeringAuthority
comment: The name of the entity authorised to collect and/or verify user details for the issual of a digital certificate.

label: licensePlate
comment: The vehicle registration number corresponding to this observation.

label: validTill
comment: The specific period of time during which a document, authorization, offer or permission remains legally or effectively acceptable/applicable.

label: modelInfo
comment: The make/model information of the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: deviceInfo
comment: The information of the device/sensor used in/for the entity/ service  corresponding to this observation.

label: range
comment: The distance upto which the vehicle is efficiently operational.

label: endurance
comment: Number of hours the drone can fly without refuelling.

label: wingSpan
comment: The maximum extent across the wings of the drone, measured from tip to tip

label: wingLength
comment: The length of the wing of the drone corresponding to this observation

label: weight
comment: The weight of the entity corresponding to this observation

label: flightAltitude
comment: The vertical distance or height above a specific reference point, usually the Mean Sea Level (MSL) or a defined datum such as WGS 84 CRS (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_Geodetic_System).

label: ownershipType
comment: The type of ownership of the entity corresponding to this observation. ENUM: [Lease, Rent, Own]

label: ownerInfo
comment: Details of the person who owns the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: lessorInfo
comment: Details of the person who leases the entity corresponding to this observation.

label: identityInfo
comment: Personal identification informations issued by the government.

label: localeInfo
comment: Locale information corresponding to this observation.

label: registrationDate
comment: The date on which a particular item or entity becomes officially recognized, authorized or approved according to the relevant regulations, procedures or requirements.

label: droneCategory
comment: The category of the drone corresponding to this observation.

label: droneCapacity
comment: The maximum weight or load that a drone, can carry or transport.
